hts-and-perspectives.html&quot;>;看起来有点不稳定&lt;/a>;。每个人都是游戏玩家，游戏正在获胜。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2ALyPq&quot;>;然而，在某些方面，业界最大、最重要的游戏似乎有些危险。即使是游戏行业的负责人，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.polygon.com/23885593/xbox-leaks-aaa-games-phil-spencer&quot;>;像微软的 Phil Spencer&lt;/a>; 也这么认为。 AAA...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23969002/fortnite-gta-vi-aaa-games-future-podcast&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23969002/fortnite-gta-vi-aaa-games-future-podcast" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23969002/fortnite-gta-vi-aaa-games-future-podcast</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-20T09:40:16-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-20T09:40:16-05:00</updated><title> CoinDesk 被加密货币交易所看涨收购</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;数字硬币着火的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EIfDwJg06-2R8EjMdJlTdwuFJUc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72884239/acastro_220524_STK428_0003 .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MEHE89&quot;>;FTX 崩溃导致 &lt;em>;CoinDesk&lt;/em>; 母公司陷入财务困境，加密货币新闻网站被收购。 Bullish，由纽约证券交易所前总裁 Tom Farley 运营的加密货币交易所，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20231120856497/en/Bullish-Acquires-CoinDesk-from-Digital-Currency -Group/?feedref=JjAwJuNHiystnCoBq_hl-W8j9Oi60kFTomUxRDB8jhBsNpnJw7dvSfTyni2BOVIOrCOi9QzgjCezTS3Nw_X6kJUrpSBm-Hav1w-UkdSlG3nDlC87j5HoE75BMeA8LaVacVjEfZIyq gxRRsuxHCTK2w%3D%3D&amp;amp;utm_source=dlvr.it&amp;amp;utm_medium=twitter&quot;>;以未公开的全现金交易购买了整个网站&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href= “https://www.wsj.com/finance/currencies/company-led-by-former-nyse-president-buys-crypto-news-site-coindesk-af3b5cc2?mod=followamazon&quot;>;首先由 &lt;em>; 报道&lt;/em>; &lt;em>;华尔街日报&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XyO1un&quot;>;此次收购不会影响&lt;em>;CoinDesk&lt;/em>;现有管理层团队，该商店“作为 Bullish 内部的独立子公司”运营。 &lt;em>;CoinDesk&